name: Flipkart - Electronic items prices
description:
**Intention** : To predict the future prices of each item and also to monitor how prices manipulated by each day. 

Mobile prices extracted from flipkart a day before big billion days.
Dataset consists of name, description, created date, offer price, original prices, ratings, reviews, item links and images.

Will try to update dataset till end of the sale.

### Categories
- Mobiles, Laptops, Tvs, Tablets, Earbuds, HDD, SSD, Pen drives, Power banks, Memory cards, Monitors, Wired Headsets, ac's, fridges, smart watchs, washing machines, water purifiers

### Columns

- name - Name of the item
- offer_price - Current price with offer
- original_price - Orginal price of the item without any offer
- off_now - % of off on item
- total_ratings - Number of ratings given 
- total_reviews - Number of reviews written
- rating - Final rating
- description - Description of the product
- created_at - Dataset created time
- u_id - Unique id
- item_link - link of the particular item

Each category  consists around 400 to 950 records and images
